OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780071066
OL,3,CFour men involved in major drugs
OL,4,Cnetwork jailed
OL,6,FFour men have been jailed for a
OL,7,Fcombined total of over 23 years for
OL,8,Ftheir involvement in a Reading drugs
OL,9,Fnetwork which police estimate was
OL,10,Finvolved in selling almost #2 million
OL,11,Fworth of drugs in the space of 20
OL,12,Fmonths.
OL,14,FThe defendants were involved in
OL,15,Frunning the 'Junior' drugs line, which
OL,16,Fpolice found had sold approximately
OL,17,F34.2kg worth of drugs between April
OL,18,F2024 and December 2025.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
