OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780071066
OL,3,CFour men involved in major drugs
OL,4,Cnetwork jailed
OL,6,FA total of #22,000 in cash was also
OL,7,Ffound at properties in Tadley, Calcot
OL,8,Fand Reading.
OL,10,FThe group was identified after a grey
OL,11,FFord Kuga failed to stop for police on
OL,12,F31 August 2025. The driver, later
OL,13,Fidentified as Cox, drove 72mph in a
OL,14,F30mph zone and ran red lights before
OL,15,Ffleeing the car and discarding three
OL,16,Fphones, which were later found by
OL,17,Fofficers to be connected to the Junior
OL,18,Fdrugs line.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
