CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780071066
OL,3,CFour men involved in major drugs
OL,4,Cnetwork jailed
OL,6,FThroughout the course of the
OL,7,Finvestigation, a series of warrants
OL,8,Fwere carried out on 9 December 2025 at
OL,9,Faddresses in West Berkshire and
OL,10,FHampshire, uncovering a number of
OL,11,Fphones being used to supply Class A
OL,12,Fdrugs, large quantities of cash,
OL,13,Fknuckle dusters and Class A and B
OL,14,Fdrugs.
OL,16,FJordan Cox, 31, of Blackbird Close in
OL,17,FBurghfield Common was jailed for ten-
OL,18,Fand-a half-years.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
