OL,3,CFour men involved in major drugs
OL,4,Cnetwork jailed
OL,6,FPierre Atangana, 31, of Woodville
OL,7,FCourt in Reading, was sentenced to six
OL,8,Fyears behind bars after pleading
OL,9,Fguilty to two counts of being
OL,10,Fconcerned in the supply of a Class A
OL,11,Fdrug, namely heroin and crack cocaine,
OL,12,Facquiring criminal property and
OL,13,Fpossession with intent to supply
OL,14,Fheroin, possession with intent to
OL,15,Fsupply cocaine and possession with
OL,16,Fintent to supply cannabis.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
