OL,3,CFour men involved in major drugs
OL,4,Cnetwork jailed
OL,6,FRobbie Parmenter, 24, of Tunworth Mews
OL,7,Fin Tadley, was sentenced to five years
OL,8,Fin prison after pleading guilty to
OL,9,Facquiring criminal property, two
OL,10,Fcounts of being concerned in the
OL,11,Fsupply of Class A drugs, namely heroin
OL,12,Fand crack cocaine, and breaching a
OL,13,Fsuspended sentence.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
