PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780071066
OL,3,CFour men involved in major drugs
OL,4,Cnetwork jailed
OL,6,FThomas Aspel, aged 27, of Delafield
OL,7,FDrive in Calcot, was jailed for two
OL,8,Fyears after pleading guilty to
OL,9,Fpossession with intent to supply
OL,10,Fheroin, possession with intent to
OL,11,Fsupply crack cocaine, acquiring
OL,12,Fcriminal property and possession of an
OL,13,Foffensive weapon in a private place.
OL,15,FInvestigating officer, Police
OL,16,FConstable Liam Steele of Reading's
OL,17,FProactive Team, said: "These sentences
OL,18,Fhave made a significant dent in
OL,19,Fharmful Class A drug supply in Reading
OL,20,Fand has disrupted serious and
OL,21,Forganised crime in the town.
OL,26,@yD@WOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
