OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780071066
OL,3,CFour men involved in major drugs
OL,4,Cnetwork jailed
OL,6,F"The supply of drugs causes harm and
OL,7,Fmisery within our communities and
OL,8,Fexploits vulnerable people.
OL,10,F"Taking such a significant amount of
OL,11,Fcrack cocaine, cocaine and heroin off
OL,12,Four streets will reduce that harm and
OL,13,Fmisery.
OL,15,F"We are committed to reducing the
OL,16,Flevels of serious and organised crime
OL,17,Fin Reading and our team will continue
OL,18,Fto target and prosecute offenders.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
