PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780071066
OL,3,CFour men involved in major drugs
OL,4,Cnetwork jailed
OL,6,F"Our activity will be both visible and
OL,7,Fcovert, aimed at disrupting and
OL,8,Fpursuing those involved in drug supply.
OL,10,F"No-one knows their streets, towns and
OL,11,Fvillages better than the people who
OL,12,Flive and work there. If you see
OL,13,Fsomething happening that is out of
OL,14,Fplace, then report it. Information we
OL,15,Freceive from the public can be vital
OL,16,Fin developing intelligence into a
OL,17,Fproactive investigation."
OL,26,@rD@AOUyD@YO]
